ing: 1 (12 ounce) package frozen edamame (green soybeans), thawed
1 (10 ounce) can whole kernel corn, drained
des: "Instead of using lima beans I like to use soybeans to make a succotash."
ins: Heat oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Add the onion, corn and soy beans, and cook until lightly browned, stirring frequently. Season to taste with seasoned salt.
